title.37: The Mutant Misadventures of Cloak and Dagger (1988) #4

description.3: Conan must fight an entire tribe of Kro warriors to be free!
description.4: Military commandos ""Sudden Impact"" flip the entire script on Death's Head in an explosive showdown!
description.5: The return of Venom! After breaking out of the Vault, Spider-Man's most pervasive foe makes his bid for vengeance. How's Hydro-Man involved? Plus, Peter makes an unsettling discovery about Aunt May's beau!
description.6: Quasar impresses Captain America after he saves Hawkeye in battle with Super-Nova. The East and West Coast Avengers agree to regroup as one team. Mr. Fantastic convinces Super-Nova to take his rage elsewhere, and search for Nebula in the timestream. Captain America makes a formal bid for Quasar to join the team.
description.7: When Darkstar, Ursa, and Vangaurd fall into a coma after being betrayed by the other Soviet Super Soldiers, Captain America must travel to Russia to stop what would be the next World War!
description.11: When Tony Stark makes a business trip to Hong Kong, he’s quit to find himself in the middle of a murder investigation. Can Iron Man get to the bottom of this heinous act of violence? Or will his search lead him right in to the clutches of the Mandarin?
description.12: Whle searching for answers about the clones of himself and Gwen Stacy, Spider-Man comes face to face with a new foe known only as Carrion!
description.13: The Bonehead Gang conflict comes to a head when Speedball and the police get involved. But the NYPD may have underestimated Bonehead’s reach and strength!
description.15: New York City caves under the demonic terror of Inferno. A dentist goes mad; children become nightmarish visions from Hell. What is Daredevil to do but save his city from insanity?
description.16: New York City falls to madness! Can Captain Britain and Kitty save themselves from the Goblin Princess- A.K.A. their teammate Meggan? Meanwhile, Nightcrawler has a wedding to crash, but as whose expense?
description.17: Maggia's goons have been genetically enhanced, making it all the more interesting for the people betting on the fight against Mr. Fixit!
description.20: Thor has defeated both Quicksand and the Mongoose before--but never at the same time! Can the Thunder God hold off this villainous alliance?
description.24: Silver Surfer is back! Returning to Earth after finding the Human Torch in space, Silver Surfer is reunited with the woman he had grown to love and thought he lost and teams up with Mantis and The Fantastic Four to fight Kang!
description.27: Thanks to his power cosmic, the Surfer is a match for just about anybody this side of Galactus. But will his power be enough when he encounters Ego, the Living Planet?
description.28: Note: this issue does not collect reprinted material from UNCANNY X-MEN (1963) #126. ""Shreds of Humanity."" How can the X-Men stop a villain who has the very fabric of reality at his fingertips? Wolverine and Nightcrawler weather the onslaught of Proteus, but will they be able to stop him?
description.29: Punisher returns to the war zone to take out Sniper, the ex-vet madman who's been killing members of his Vietnam unit. But will Frank Castle be the next hit? The armory's locked and loaded, and so is the Punisher.
description.30: When Peter and Mary Jane Parker's neighbor kidnapped MJ, they had him arrested. But now, he's wreaked his vengeance...by evicting them from their home! Could there be a Christmas miracle in store for everybody's favorite wall-crawler?
description.31: Super-Nova is plummeting towards Earth seeking vengeance against Nebula. However, little does he know, Nebula has been lost in the time stream. The East Coast Avengers must placate an angry Super-Nova until the West Coast team arrives to save the day.
description.32: The Soviet Super Soldiers Vanguard, Darkstar and Ursa Major want to defect to America. Find out what happens as Steve Rogers come faces-to-face with Soviet Union!
description.33: Hawkeye teams up with the Sandman to stop Doctor Octopus from getting his tentacles on a deadly weapon!  Plus, Sub-Mariner in solo action!
description.37: Cloak and Dagger are hunted by demons so that they can be used in a spell! Thankfully, Warlock, Dani Moonstar, Boom Boom, Sunspot and Gosamyr of the New Mutants are tracking these same demons to save Cloak and Dagger!
description.42: Conon ventures to the city of shadows in search of treasure!
description.43: The freelance hustle of taking lives gets a serious pickup when Death's Head is offered half a shipment of gold bullion!
description.44: In the aftermath to the INFERNO event, Julie Power must reconcile with growing up!
description.45: Total Pan-DEMON-ium! Doctor Strange is nearly overwhelmed by the demonic horde, but he's not alone in this fight! Guest-starring the New Defenders!
description.47: Mania rules over New York City after the Owl's plan to usurp a drug ring turns violent. Will Daredevil be able to save the life of a baby amidst the chaos? And simultaneously take down the Owl?
description.48: Jacob Burnley has begun to learn to control his Star Brand power, and he's decided it's time to take action! His first target - the President of the United States!?
description.49: Spidey travels to the sewers of New York City to rescue MJ and her camera crew from the demons who have invaded their shoot…and the Hobgoblin is quick to follow!
description.50: An INFERNO side-story! Demons are on the loose in NYC, and two particularly malevolent spirits have set their sights on Betty Brant and Flash Thompson!
description.51: Robbie deals with a new love interest while feeling under the weather, but that fiasco can’t compare to the frosty bite of Bonehead!
description.53: The team gets a rude welcome in New York City- inanimate objects are running amok and the Empire State Building appears to be...growing?
description.54: Mr. Maggia sends his goons to take out Michael Berenguetti. But Mr. Fixit is on site to sort the goons out!
description.55: The Ghost has proven to be too strong for the likes of one hero! So how about one hero and and four villains? That's right! Iron Man teams up with his enemies to battle the Ghost! Don't miss the final showdown.
description.58: A tale of brothers' past! 1000 years ago, Loki wagers Thor that he cannot survive a dangerous quest without Mjolnir! Thor accepts, but Loki has no intention of playing fair...
description.61: The Fantastic Four versus Kang the Conqueror! Can the FF save their friend, the hero Mantis, from the clutches of the time-traveling madman!
description.64: The Obliterator is back looking for revenge! And what better way for him to get back at the Silver Surfer than by destroying his home world, Zenn-La!
description.65: Note: this issue does not collect reprinted material from UNCANNY X-MEN (1963) #125. ""Spigot at the End of the Universe."" Struggling and dissatisfied in his role as Empress Lilandra's consort, Charles Xavier learns an important lesson from Throneworld's plumber.
description.66: Daredevil pulls Punisher's fat from the fire after the vigilante gets a deadly dose of Montoya's poison. But how will Jason Hunt escape the mobster's grasp? Plus, the origin of Hector Montoya. Who is the mastermind responsible for a trail of death as bloody as it is wide?
description.69: Things were looking good for Doctor Curt Connors. After years of monstrous transformations, he had finally gained control over his reptilian alter ego. But when Inferno strikes, the lethal Lizard goes wild!
description.70: The new Avengers decide to set up permanent shop at the Hydrobase in New York Harbor. But just as team settles into their new digs, a galactic threat from Nebula arrives!
description.71: Captain America and Nick Fury team up to knock out a top-secret SHIELD base. But if you've been following NICK FURY VS. S.H.I.E.L.D. you know something about this mission is pretty fishy!
description.77: All Conan wanted was to steal the Zeddite cult's jeweled sacrificial blade. But now the entire cult is after him— and they want his blood! Will Conan lose his life to "The Blade of Zed"?
description.78: What do a birthday cake and a feral dog have in common? Both are featured in this issue!
description.81: The effects of INFERNO hit the world of Spider-Man! Peter's pal Harry Osborn is in grave danger at his chemical plant!
description.82: A notorious public villain suddenly, and forcefully, shows up in Robbie’s life!
description.83: A day of reckoning for one of the West Coast Avengers! Mockingbird has been endlessly tormented by the enigmatic Phantom Rider, and their conflict at last comes to a head here! Is the Rider friend or foe? And what is his connection to Moon Knight?
description.87: Daredevil may be recovering in a hospital, but he's not out of the woods yet! Karen discovers Matt's affair with Mary...in the middle of a demon invasion!
description.88: The team, still trapped in Murderworld, is attacked by strange machinations of Arcade's mind. Courtney Ross stars in an 'Alice in Wonderland' fantasy courtesy of the Crazy Gang and Arcade. Brian reaches a critical decision in his love life.
description.89: The Wizard that snatched up the Hulk has dropped him in a magical land. Now the Hulk must put a stop to the Inquisitor!
description.90: He's back! And this time the Ghost is out for blood! Is the Iron Avenger prepared for the paranormal?
description.93: Thor's great battle sprawls across all of time and space as he clashes with the vile Surtur! All-Father Odin confronts Surtur to take back his realm once and for all! This is it: Asgard's greatest battle and most dire crisis!
description.94: Peter discovers a feral Harry before the two are attacked by the Hobgoblin!
description.97: When Mantis is kidnapped by Kang as part of his plan to awaken the Dreaming Celestial, the Fantastic Four spring into action to rescue the Celestial Madonna!

0.text: Frank Castle goes international in the Land Down Under! What new trouble has brought Punisher to the heart of the Outback?

1.text: When Katie's favorite writer is a suspect in a robbery, she goes to the Punisher for justice!

2.text: Slippery Sam protects a child. The Wolfpack uncovers that more school age children than ever are starting to experiment with drugs and are forming more gangs.

11.text: When Tony Stark makes a business trip to Hong Kong, he’s quit to find himself in the middle of a murder investigation. Can Iron Man get to the bottom of this heinous act of violence? Or will his search lead him right in to the clutches of the Mandarin?

12.text: Whle searching for answers about the clones of himself and Gwen Stacy, Spider-Man comes face to face with a new foe known only as Carrion!

13.text: The Bonehead Gang conflict comes to a head when Speedball and the police get involved. But the NYPD may have underestimated Bonehead’s reach and strength!

14.text: Contains only Panther’s Quest Part 5: Reasonable Force. PANTHER’S QUEST PART 5: En route to his hidden glider, T’Challa and Zanti are detained by a pair of soldiers.

18.text: Contains only Panther’s Quest Part 4: The Man Who Loved Sunrise. PANTHER’S QUEST PART 4: A badly beaten T’Challa struggles to reach his sonar glider with the help of a local miner named Zanti Chikane.

19.text: Aftermath to Inferno! What will be left of the X-mansion by the end of this issue?

22.text: Mr. Sinister and Cyclops' twisted history is revealed as their destructive showdown comes to a head. Can Cyclops' surpass the artificial limitations that Sinister has imposed upon him?
Mr. Sinister and Cyclops' twisted history is revealed as their destructive showdown comes to a head. Can Cyclops' surpass the artificial limitations that Sinister has imposed upon him?

25.text: While Beast and Longshot get people to safety, Jean Grey battles Mr. Sinister on the psychic plane! As Sinister attempts to destroy every single memory that Jean has, Jean must integrate the personalities of both the Phoenix and Madelyne.

While Beast and Longshot get people to safety, Jean Grey battles Mr. Sinister on the psychic plane! As Sinister attempts to destroy every single memory that Jean has, Jean must integrate the personalities of both the Phoenix and Madelyne.

26.text: The Harriers step in as the crime war between Tyger Tiger and General Coy heats up! The only way to tell the good guys from the bad guys is to watch who Wolverine throws down on!

34.text: Scarlet Witch is seething, and her vengeance is mighty; the West Coast Avengers find Vision at a Vigilance base, where he is the latest science experiment of Cameron Brock. Will the Avengers be able to prevent a dissection of their android teammate? Find out in 'To Rescue the Vision'!

35.text: With his memory restored, Sub-Mariner’s wartime adventures are revisited!

36.text: Super heroes may be taking names and laying punches in the midst of Acts of Vengeance, but Mrs. Hoag and Albert Cleary have their own war to wage! Will Damage Control fall under new ownership? Not if the loyal office staff has their say!

38.text: There's good news for the Morituri - Dr. Tuolema has found a cure to the fatal process that gave them heir powers! But they may never get a chance to try it out, because the latest generation of Morituri are out to kill their predecessors!

39.text: Peace talks are in progress in Paris, and that means a little R&R's in store for the troops. But even rest and relaxation isn't all it's cracked up to be in the perilous world of the 'NAM!

40.text: At long last! Wilson Fisk and Frank Castle have their much-anticipated showdown. But should Kingpin die, will Punisher be responsible for igniting the next great gang war?

41.text: With a member of the Wolfpack stepping down and another injured in the hospital, will the crew be able to defeat the savage street gangs of South Bronx?

45.text: Total Pan-DEMON-ium! Doctor Strange is nearly overwhelmed by the demonic horde, but he's not alone in this fight! Guest-starring the New Defenders!

51.text: Robbie deals with a new love interest while feeling under the weather, but that fiasco can’t compare to the frosty bite of Bonehead!

52.text: Contains only Panther's Quest Part 3: Lost Blood In Copper Dust. PANTHER’S QUEST PART 3: T’Challa and Slade must escape from the clutches of Elmer Gore’s mercenaries.

56.text: Contains only Panther's Quest Part 2: Forgotten Corpses. PANTHER’S QUEST PART 2: During T’Challa’s meeting with Patrick Slade, the two are ambushed by Elmer Gore’s mercenaries.

57.text: While Magik battles S'ym, Cannonball, Sunspot, Rictor, and Warlock engage in a desperate search for her. Will they find Magik before tragedy befalls her? Meanwhile, Mirage, Rusty, and Skids do their best to protect Artie, Leech, and the babies.

While Magik battles S'ym, Cannonball, Sunspot, Rictor, and Warlock engage in a desperate search for her. Will they find Magik before tragedy befalls her? Meanwhile, Mirage, Rusty, and Skids do their best to protect Artie, Leech, and the babies.

59.text: The origin of Madelyne Prior stands revealed! Why does she want revenge on Cyclops? Who orchestrated the events of her life? Plus, Jean Grey is given an ultimatum by the Phoenix itself!
The origin of Madelyne Prior stands revealed! Why does she want revenge on Cyclops? Who orchestrated the events of her life? Plus, Jean Grey is given an ultimatum by the Phoenix itself!

62.text: The X-Men defend the Goblyn Queen-who is disguised as Maddie-from X-Factor! Can the two teams discover the queen's ruse in time to stop her?
The X-Men defend the Goblyn Queen-who is disguised as Maddie-from X-Factor! Can the two teams discover the queen's ruse in time to stop her?

63.text: The Harriers step in as the crime war between Tyger Tiger and General Coy heats up! The only way to tell the good guys from the bad guys is to watch who Wolverine throws down on!

67.text: Mockingbird makes her triumphant return to the West Coast! But as one teammate appears, another goes missing. Where is the Vision?

68.text: Here come the Invaders! Sub-Mariner joins the Human Torch, Captain America, Bucky and Toro to take down members of the Third Reich.

72.text: It's been a long time since Hawkeye and the Black Widow fought as a team. But now, it looks like they may die together unless they can find a way to thwart the plans of A.I.M.! Also featuring a story starring Galactic Avenger, Moondragon!

73.text: There are some surprises in store as Doctor Tuolema reviews the entire history of the Morituri Process from its original discovery up to the present. But he'd better finish quickly -- the most recent recipients of the Morituri powers are on their way to kill him!

74.text: Attempting to cut off a shipment of supplies, the men of the 23rd face a fateful choice: will they cross the forbidden border into Cambodia or be killed by the Viet Cong convoy they've ambushed?

75.text: Ante up! Punisher has eliminated Kingpin’s deadliest assassin…and now he’s gunning to topple Kingpin’s casino!

76.text: Missionary is hired to go after Wolfpack and Sharon’s spine is injured by a shot. Then, Missionary joins forces with Wolfpack and goes after Nine’s operation heads!

79.text: Sensational She-Hulk to the rescue! In the aftermath to Acts of Vengeance, Damage Control calls in back-up from the Jade Giantess. But what begins as a clean-up ends as a riot. Is She-Hulk to blame for the labor union’s discord?

80.text: An Inferno tie-in. It won't be easy for Power Pack to help the New Mutants wrap up Inferno. But that's going to be a breeze compared to facing their parents, now that their folks know about their dual identities!

81.text: The effects of INFERNO hit the world of Spider-Man! Peter's pal Harry Osborn is in grave danger at his chemical plant!

82.text: A notorious public villain suddenly, and forcefully, shows up in Robbie’s life!

83.text: A day of reckoning for one of the West Coast Avengers! Mockingbird has been endlessly tormented by the enigmatic Phantom Rider, and their conflict at last comes to a head here! Is the Rider friend or foe? And what is his connection to Moon Knight?

86.text: Contains only Panther's Quest: A Rumor of Life. PANTHER’S QUEST PART 1: T’Challa meets with Patrick Slade for information about his mother Ramonda!

92.text: Magik has become the Darkchilde! While she battles N'astirh in her new form, the New Mutants are left to fend for themselves against a band of demons. Will Cannonball and his team be able to survive this otherworldly onslaught?

Magik has become the Darkchilde! While she battles N'astirh in her new form, the New Mutants are left to fend for themselves against a band of demons. Will Cannonball and his team be able to survive this otherworldly onslaught?

95.text: The Goblyn Queen has the child that Cyclops is searching for. Can the help of the X-Men be enough to usher the child to safety or will it perish in the hands of the queen?
he Goblyn Queen has the child that Cyclops is searching for. Can the help of the X-Men be enough to usher the child to safety or will it perish in the hands of the queen?

98.text: As the X-Men begin to undergo demonic transformations of their own, Colossus separates from the group to find his sister Magik.
As the X-Men begin to undergo demonic transformations of their own, Colossus separates from the group to find his sister Magik.

99.text: Introducing Bloodsport and Roughouse, the odd couple of immortal monsterdom! They're working for Wolverine's enemies - the question is, is ex-New Mutant Karma doing the same?
